---
---
<section id="casestudies" class="section-pad" style="padding-top: calc(var(--space-xl) * 1.5); padding-bottom: calc(var(--space-xl) * 1.5);">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl);">Verified <span class="text-accent">Impact</span></h2>
    <p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: var(--text-lg); max-width: 70ch;">Real-world execution. We don't just build software pipelines; we engineer direct improvements to your bottom line.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg);">
    
    <!-- Flagship Case Study -->
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
      <div style="background-color: var(--color-accent); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-sm); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">
        Enterprise Contract Intelligence
      </div>
      <div style="padding: var(--space-lg); display: grid; gap: var(--space-lg); align-items: center;" class="case-study-split">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Orange Unified School District</h3>
          <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-text-main); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Real-time contract performance and efficiency automation mapping $1.85M in annual spend.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
            OUSD suffered from fragmented data between student enrollment metrics and IT vendor contracts. We implemented a unified <strong>Contract Intelligence Dashboard</strong> that algorithmically analyzed usage against spend over a 5-year period.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
            Our AI analysis identified a critical "Value Delta": While district ADA (Average Daily Attendance) dropped 13.9%, vendor spend on the Aeries SIS contract ballooned by 158%. 
          </p>
          <div style="border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
            <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: var(--text-2xl); color: var(--color-text-main);">$127,000+ Identified Overpayment</div>
            <div style="font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase;">Immediate Renegotiation Workflow Generated</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="background: var(--color-secondary); border-radius: 12px; padding: var(--space-md); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <div style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-main);">Dashboard Telemetry Analyzed</div>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: var(--text-sm);">
            <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
              <span style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Total Analyzed Spend</span>
              <strong style="color: var(--color-text-main);">$1.85M</strong>
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
              <span style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Active Vendors Audited</span>
              <strong style="color: var(--color-text-main);">23</strong>
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
              <span style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Value Delta Detected</span>
              <strong style="color: #ef4444;">172.5%</strong>
            </li>
            <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;">
              <span style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Automation Feature</span>
              <strong style="color: var(--color-text-main);">AI Renegotiation Drafts</strong>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Brief Case Studies -->
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-md);">
      
      <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: var(--space-md);">
        <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #DCFCE7; color: #166534; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"></polyline><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 style="font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Agency Growth Engine</h4>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Replaced manual SDR team with fully orchestrated multi-channel AI sequences. Led directly to 300%+ pipeline growth inside of two business quarters.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: var(--space-md);">
        <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #F3E8FF; color: #6B21A8; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 style="font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Security Vendor Auditing</h4>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Automated checking against 18 expired tech contracts operating without valid security agreements, instantly mitigating critical backend risk for the IT department.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <style>
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .case-study-split {
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
